gov.nih.nci.cbiit.cmts.ui.util
Class MappingViewCommonComponent

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nci.cbiit.cmts.ui.util.MappingViewCommonComponent
All Implemented Interfaces:
PropertiesProvider, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable
public class MappingViewCommonComponent
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable, java.io.Serializable, PropertiesProvider

A data container contains mapping information, which is the mapping either from-tree-to-functional-box, from-functional-box-to-tree, or from-functional-box-to-functional-box, or direct-tree-to-tree mapping. This data container may act like a bridge between JGraph data structure and HL7SDK internal data structure so as to keep each in sync with the other. This data is also served as the user object of the linkEdge object, so as to provide properties information on linkage. This is an immutable class and mainly participate in the mapping cache for rendering purpose.

Since:
CMTS v1.0
